race.comment: MEET ME IN BONDI (3) kept safe in betting on his return when knocked up late to finish fourth over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Gets a better set-up for this with a key jockey change. Ready to win. MIGNONETTE (8) two runs back have been okay, and she gets out to her right distance range today. Warmed up late when sixth over 1350m at Wyong. Genuine top three player. TEQUISODA (5) improving colt who can go on with it this time in. Returned good closing splits on resumption when a sound third over 1400m at Kembla Grange. Reith sticks and suited on the roomier track. GOLDEN LOOM (2) set to peak and doesn't have to improve much to take this out. Came from last on the turn when third over 1500m at Kembla Grange. Gets his chance. SUPREME STATEMENT (6) well weighted with the claim and comes here in peak condition.
